Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:09.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hosu General Hospital"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days since the Hosu incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and five days since\Nwe started our internships...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since my injuries from Stain were not\Nfully healed yet, I was in a hospital bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Special Report: Hero Killer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the news, the hero killer\Nwas the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:28.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Near the scene the day after the incident"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When seven pro heroes and three high school\Nstudents came across the hero killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endeavor rushed over\Nand took care of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the official story\Nreleased by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the person from the police said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida, Todoroki,\Nand my names were not made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our injuries were explained away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as accidents that happened \Nduring our internships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night Iida got the results of\Nthe examination of his injured arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:56.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tenya Iida - Quirk: Engine"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he went back with his mom \Nto his parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Izuku Midoriya - Quirk: One For All"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Todoroki,\Nwho had relatively light injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shoto Todoroki - Quirk: Half-Cold, Half-Hot"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return to my internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Endeavor's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn what I can from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, they said he defeated the\Nhero killer even though he didn't actually do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see his expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You become kind of mean when\Nit comes to Endeavor, huh, Todoroki?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure everyone else\Nis working hard right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone's Internships"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is possible that the villains who were\Ninspired by the Hosu incident the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will become more active.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this is just a patrol,\Ndon't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sudden, but here's a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patrols are meant to deter\Nvillains from committing crimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:28.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katsuki Bakugo - Quirk: Explosion"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they also have a secondary effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we see villains, we \Nbeat them up right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Best Jeanist"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Best Jeanist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is: to show people who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To give the public peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It builds trust between those who\Nprotect and those who are being protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, a courtesy visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've seen him on TV before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sports festival again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was caught by a villain and\Nlooked like he was about to cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already forget what I taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I wasn't caught\Nby the villain back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about how to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that I'd lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who'll become \Nthe number one hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for kids\Nlike you to worry about me--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine for those strong feelings\Nto be aimed at becoming a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if that is no longer the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what shall I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Gunhead"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would you fight against\Nan opponent with a knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uravity, can you try attacking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ochaco Uraraka - Quirk: Zero Gravity"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone's waving a knife at you,\Ndeal with it by keeping your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they attack directly,\Nuse one leg as an axis to turn and dodge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then grab their wrist\Nand neck and the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then hold them down \Nas you pull their wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can twist their wrist\Nto make them drop the knife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and kick the knife far away,\Nit'll be even more perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He moved so smoothly, without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunhead Martial Arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he acts cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll hold the knife, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep repeating this \Nuntil you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Uwabami, can I have your autograph?\N--Can I take your picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Uwabami"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you work diligently like this,\Nyou can eventually make big blossoms bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:55.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Momo Yaoyorozu - Quirk: Creation"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like when an {\i1}enka{\i0} singer\Ngoes on provincial tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't "work diligently"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mean something different?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Itsuka Kendo - Quirk: Big Fist"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Fourth Kind"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contributing to the community is\Nalso an essential part of being a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag your feet doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. Fourth Kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tetsutetsu Tetsutetsu - Quirk: Steel"\N"Eijiro Kirishima - Quirk: Hardening"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mr. Fourth Kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Death Arms"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many hostages are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I can hear, there are two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyoka Jiro - Quirk: Earphone Jack"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We're breaking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earphone Jack, please tell\Nthe escaping hostages what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, Death Arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pro hero! Do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will escort you! Come below with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:49.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oki Mariner"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsuyu Asui - Quirk: Frog"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished cleaning the deck, Sirius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring just training and\Ncleaning the deck every day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same when I did my internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was confused by the difference \Nbetween the image I had of what a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was when I was a kid and \Nwhat the reality was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagined something a lot showier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality, it's a daily grind\Nof training and patrols and cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I even had\Nto wash the captain's underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is being a hero? I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get tired of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after becoming the\Ncaptain's sidekick, I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what was really important for a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's really important? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to find the answer to that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Froppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you playing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because frogs have big mouths doesn't\Nmean you can spend all your time gabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sirius, I ordered you to supervise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you're doing your job properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished cleaning, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm supervising her properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see! My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I too cute for words, Froppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always say this, but you\Ncan't just make your face cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Below the neck, you're too macho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is also too rugged, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I do this for kids, they love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They love making fun of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's not cute {\i1}at all{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Selkie, there's a message\Nfrom the Japan Coast Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll be there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy, help me unfasten the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably be sailing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You're good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ropes are unfastened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailors! We're making an emergency departure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aye aye, sir!\N--Aye aye, sir!\N--Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the {\i1}Oki Mariner{\i0} is sailing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"Affiliation: U.A. High School Hero Class 1-A"\N"Birthday: 8/1" "Height: 154 cm"\N "Blood Type: A" "Likes: Rock Music"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kyoka Jiro"\N"Quirk: Earphone Jack"\N"She can insert the plugs on her earlobes into her opponent and channel loud sounds into them."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}"Affiliation: U.A. High School Hero Class 1-A"\N"Birthday: 2/12" "Height: 150 cm"\N "Blood Type: B" "Likes: Jello"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsuyu Asui"\N"Quirk: Frog"\N"She can do pretty much everything a frog can, like stretch out her tongue really far."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stowaways?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Coast Guard got a tip that there\Nwere stowaways on the trade ship, {\i1}Nysan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Coast Guard inspected the {\i1}Nysan{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\but the stowaways were nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after more careful investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they found cargo missing\Nfrom the ship's freight list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what this means, Froppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it means that\Nbefore the Coast Guard arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stowaways moved the cargo\Nto another ship and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stowaways may have \Nbeen smuggling brokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The job we've taken on this time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to secure the stowaways\Nthought to have escaped on a small boat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and deliver them to the Coast Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the {\i1}Nysan{\i0}'s position,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is the area of the ocean where\Nthe smaller boat is predicted to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Coast Guard and other sea rescue\Nheroes are also searching for the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be responsible for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will set soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys search for the boat with the radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will look for them in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get to work, sailors!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aye aye, sir!\N--Aye aye, sir!\N--Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:23.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Selkie"\N"Quirk: Spotted Seal"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Rescue Hero: Selkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quirk: Spotted Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can do pretty much\Nanything a spotted seal can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can even make a sonar-like sound
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and use the echo to determine\Nthe position of his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll widen my search a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, I can't see\Nanything in this darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like we've been able\Nto catch anything on the radar yet, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the captain on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a message from the Coast Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishing boat thought to belong to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stowaways shook off \Na hero agency patrol boat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and escaped into the direction\Nof the area we're in charge of!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've confirmed the location of the fishing\Nboat thought to belong to the stowaways!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn off all the lights and get close\Nwithout letting them know where we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aye aye, sir!\N--Aye aye, sir!\N--Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I can see a\Nfishing boat with my naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, block their \Ncourse with a patrol boat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and board their boat while \Nsetting off a flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be able\Nto experience the internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet and do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you want to go with them, Froppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, even if we're up against\Nstowaways, we have to be very careful, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So follow the captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give them support together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we've arrived\Nat the fishing boat's course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship! This is a pro hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are here on a job for the\NJapan Coast Guard to inspect your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I didn't find\Nany of the cargo in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't any here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just fishing--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you can show us\Nwhat's under here, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing but fish down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just open it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing but fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you turn on any lights--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So p... please spare my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't kill ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can buy this much time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it'll be easier for Boss Innsmouth\Nto do what he needs to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Captain, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. The radio's \Nnot getting through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:52.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sirius"\N"Quirk: Good Ear"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius! Quirk: Good Ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can hear high frequencies\Nthat humans cannot hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stowaways"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Different boat"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We're fine. Find them."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mick, start the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that boat is a decoy, then the stowaways
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should be heading toward the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to resuce\Nthe captain and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to follow the captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we believe what the captain\Ndecided is the best course of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy, you believe, too--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hiding in the shadow of Double Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, in a place like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the engine and go to\None of the cruiser's blind spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy, you help, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone keeping watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy, can you bring the guard over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Wha... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You guys--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you answer our questions,\Nthen we won't get rough with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one person on the cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hiding in a cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drag him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd gotten clean away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you guys are too persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, you've only got\Na woman and a kid left?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her back once\NI'm free of the Coast Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you help me move the cargo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're locked up in the fishing boat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and our transmission's been blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain went ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ribbit...\N--How are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your situation. Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a radio, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you care about this woman's life,\Nthen tell them this:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We couldn't find the stowaways."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Fro--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what'll happen to this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what was really important for a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to follow the captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we believe what the captain\Ndecided is the best course of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy, you believe, too--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stowaways are at Double Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving around so much! It's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oops! I've got you.\N--Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ri... Ribbit... Rib...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you came here uninvited,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.06,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. What about you, Sirius?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's the only thing strong about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we were\Nable to catch the stowaways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing that {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, I'm glad I was able\Nto come to this internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's really important for a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand a little better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest all the stowaways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to recover all the\Nillegal drugs they were trying to bring in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Selkie,\Nwhen did you get a new sidekick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a U.A. student
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here for an internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? We made you\Ngo through something scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't treat her like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy doesn't have her license yet,\Nbut she's already an excellent hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm looking forward to\Nwhen we can work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Froppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Might! I have returned \Nfrom my internship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went through a lot\Nwith the Hosu incident, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't be nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what were you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come when I must tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about me and One For All,\Nand the mission entrusted to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Listen Up!! \NA Tale from the Past."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important episode,\Nso you're not allowed to miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go beyond!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:51.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next time: Listen Up!! A Tale from the Past"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus Ultra!
